description: ***INQUIRE ABOUT HOA FEE CREDIT*** This stylish duplex city home pairs modern design with full-service amenities. The main floor features an open-plan layout with kitchen outfitted with Wolf and Sub-Zero appliances, floor-to-ceiling south-facing windows, and double-height ceilings. A flexible den off the foyer provides space for a home office, media lounge, or guest room, with a half bath and in-unit laundry for convenience. Upstairs, the primary suite offers en suite bath access, while a second full bath serves the guest bedroom. A private roof terrace spanning 440+ sq. ft. creates space for dining, entertaining, or city gardening. Building amenities include concierge and 24/7 valet garage parking, a fitness center, and easy access to downtown, Seaport, and South Station. Designed for those who appreciate modern style, flexibility, and convenience, this home offers elevated city living in a prime location.
